name: Divine Arsenal AA-Zero
effect:
5 Level 12 monsters
Must be Xyz Summoned and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. Once per Chain, when your opponent activates a card or effect (Quick Effect): You can detach 1 material from this card; negate the activation. If this Xyz Summoned card in its owner's control leaves the field by your opponent: You can activate this effect; Special Summon 1 "Divine Arsenal" monster from your hand, Deck, GY or banishment, except "Divine Arsenal AA-Zero".
